@startuml
title Marketplace Search and Filtering

|User|
start
:Open marketplace page;

|System|
:Display all available marketplace listings;

|User|
:Enter search term or select filters;

|System|
:Apply search and filter criteria;

if (Matching posts found?) then (Yes)
  :Display filtered marketplace results;
else (No)
  :Display no matching results message;
endif

|User|
if (Modify search or filters?) then (Yes)
  :Update search term or filters;
  |System|
  :Apply updated criteria;
  if (Matching posts found?) then (Yes)
    :Display filtered marketplace results;
  else (No)
    :Display no matching results message;
  endif
else (No)
endif

end
@enduml